rs in the foot of the shock front\nand at the ramp, where the reflected ions are emerging in addition to the\nupstream solar wind ions, the anisotropy growing to generate the bursts of\nion-scales electrostatic waves. The entropy of electrons across the shock\ndoesn't show significant change - electron heating goes almost adiabatically.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jun 2023 19:11:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
