lity and precision of their experimental\nprocedures, including $^{71}$Ge recovery, counting, and analysis. We also\ndescribe efforts to define uncertainties in the neutrino capture cross section.\nWith the results from BEST, an anomaly remains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jun 2023 22:49:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
